---
layout: layouts/page.njk
title: Contact FlowSync Consulting
description: Get in touch with FlowSync Consulting to discuss your NetSuite automation and integration needs.
---

<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-8 md:mb-12">
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Join companies who've eliminated 600+ hours/month of manual work and protected $500K+ in annual revenue through NetSuite automation.
        </p>
        <div class="bg-accent-light bg-opacity-10 border border-accent rounded-lg p-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            <p class="font-semibold text-primary mb-2">What to Expect from This Call</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">30-minute conversation about your challenges. No sales pressure. We'll explore if automation makes sense for your situation. Most projects: $15K-$40K, 4-8 weeks, 3-6 month payback.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Quick Contact Options -->
    <div class="mb-12 md:mb-16">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
            <!-- Schedule a Call -->
            <a href="mailto:contact@flowsyncconsulting.com?subject=NetSuite Consultation Request" class="block bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-primary-dark text-white rounded-lg p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition-all hover:scale-[1.02]">
                <div class="text-4xl mb-4">📅</div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Schedule a Call</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm mb-4">
                    30-minute discovery call to discuss your NetSuite challenges and explore solutions.
                </p>
                <div class="inline-flex items-center text-accent-light font-semibold">
                    Email to schedule
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
            </a>

            <!-- Send Message -->
            <a href="#contact-form" class="block bg-white border-2 border-primary rounded-lg p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition-all hover:scale-[1.02]">
                <div class="text-4xl mb-4">✉️</div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">Send a Message</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">
                    Share project details and budget. We'll respond within 24 hours with next steps.
                </p>
                <div class="inline-flex items-center text-accent font-semibold">
                    Fill out form below
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
            </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Contact Form -->
        <div id="contact-form" class="max-w-2xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200 p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-6 text-center">Contact Form</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-center mb-8">
                Share your NetSuite challenges. We typically respond within 24 hours.
            </p>

            <form name="contact" method="POST" data-netlify="true" netlify-honeypot="bot-field" action="/contact-success/" class="space-y-6">
                <!-- Honeypot field for spam protection -->
                <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="contact">
                <div class="hidden" aria-hidden="true">
                    <label>Don't fill this out if you're human: <input name="bot-field"></label>
                </div>

                <!-- Name -->
                <div>
                    <label for="name" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-primary mb-2">
                        Name <span class="text-red-500">*</span>
                    </label>
                    <input
                        type="text"
                        id="name"
                        name="name"
                        required
                        class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-accent focus:border-transparent transition-all"
                        placeholder="Your full name"
                    >
                </div>

                <!-- Email -->
                <div>
                    <label for="email" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-primary mb-2">
                        Email <span class="text-red-500">*</span>
                    </label>
                    <input
                        type="email"
                        id="email"
                        name="email"
                        required
                        class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-accent focus:border-transparent transition-all"
                        placeholder="you@company.com"
                    >
                </div>

                <!-- Company -->
                <div>
                    <label for="company" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-primary mb-2">
                        Company
                    </label>
                    <input
                        type="text"
                        id="company"
                        name="company"
                        class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-accent focus:border-transparent transition-all"
                        placeholder="Your company name"
                    >
                </div>

                <!-- Budget Range -->
                <div>
                    <label for="budget" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-primary mb-2">
                        Estimated Budget Range
                    </label>
                    <select
                        id="budget"
                        name="budget"
                        class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-accent focus:border-transparent transition-all bg-white"
                    >
                        <option value="">Select a range (optional)</option>
                        <option value="under-10k">Under $10,000</option>
                        <option value="10k-25k">$10,000 - $25,000</option>
                        <option value="25k-50k">$25,000 - $50,000</option>
                        <option value="50k-plus">$50,000+</option>
                        <option value="not-sure">Not sure yet</option>
                    </select>
                </div>

                <!-- Project Description -->
                <div>
                    <label for="message" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-primary mb-2">
                        Tell us about your project <span class="text-red-500">*</span>
                    </label>
                    <textarea
                        id="message"
                        name="message"
                        required
                        rows="6"
                        class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-accent focus:border-transparent transition-all resize-y"
                        placeholder="What NetSuite challenges are you facing? What outcomes are you looking for?"
                    ></textarea>
                    <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-2">
                        Include: Current pain points, manual processes, integration needs, or performance issues.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <!-- Submit Button -->
                <div class="pt-4">
                    <button
                        type="submit"
                        class="w-full btn btn-primary text-lg py-4 hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform"
                    >
                        Send Message
                    </button>
                    <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 text-center mt-3">
                        We'll respond within 24 hours on business days.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-12">
        <!-- Contact Information -->
        <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">Contact Information</h2>

            <div class="space-y-6">
                <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                    <div class="text-2xl">📍</div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-primary mb-1">Location</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">{{ site.location_display }}</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                    <div class="text-2xl">⏱️</div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-primary mb-1">Response Time</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">
                            Within 24 hours on business days<br>
                            Monday - Friday, 9 AM - 5 PM Pacific
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-10 p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-primary mb-4">Business Information</h3>
                <div class="space-y-2">
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                        <strong>Business Name:</strong> FlowSync Consulting
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                        <strong>Location:</strong> {{ site.location_display }}
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- What to Expect -->
        <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">What to Expect</h2>

            <div class="space-y-6">
                <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                    <div class="bg-accent text-white w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">1</div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-primary mb-1">Discovery Call (30 min)</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
                            We discuss your challenges, goals, and NetSuite environment. No sales pitch. If automation doesn't make sense for you, we'll tell you.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                    <div class="bg-accent text-white w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">2</div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-primary mb-1">Detailed Proposal (2-3 days)</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
                            Clear scope, timeline, pricing, and ROI estimate. Typical projects: $15K-$40K, 4-8 weeks, payback in 3-6 months.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                    <div class="bg-accent text-white w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">3</div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-primary mb-1">Build, Deploy, Train</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
                            We develop, test, deploy, and train your team. You own everything we build. Full documentation and knowledge transfer included.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-8 p-6 bg-accent-light bg-opacity-10 border border-accent rounded-lg">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-primary mb-2">Response Time</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">
                    We typically respond within <strong>24 hours</strong> on business days. For urgent matters, please note that in your message.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <section class="mt-12 md:mt-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-6 md:mb-8 text-center">Common Questions</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
            <details class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
                <summary class="font-bold text-primary cursor-pointer">What industries do you work with?</summary>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mt-3 text-sm">
                    We've delivered projects across distribution, manufacturing, financial services, insurance, apparel, and professional services. Our approach focuses on understanding business processes, not just technical requirements.
                </p>
            </details>

            <details class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
                <summary class="font-bold text-primary cursor-pointer">What's your typical project timeline?</summary>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mt-3 text-sm">
                    Small automations: 1-2 weeks. Custom Suitelets: 3-6 weeks. Integration pipelines: 4-8 weeks. Timelines depend on complexity, testing requirements, and client availability for feedback.
                </p>
            </details>

            <details class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
                <summary class="font-bold text-primary cursor-pointer">Do you provide ongoing support?</summary>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mt-3 text-sm">
                    Yes. We offer retainer-based support for ongoing development, troubleshooting, and optimization. We also provide knowledge transfer documentation so you can maintain solutions internally if preferred.
                </p>
            </details>

            <details class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
                <summary class="font-bold text-primary cursor-pointer">What's your pricing model?</summary>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mt-3 text-sm">
                    Typical projects range from $15K-$40K and take 4-8 weeks. Most pay for themselves in 3-6 months through headcount savings or revenue protection. We offer project-based (fixed scope), retainer (monthly capacity), and hourly consulting. Detailed proposals provided before any commitment.
                </p>
            </details>

            <details class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
                <summary class="font-bold text-primary cursor-pointer">Do you work with offshore teams or directly?</summary>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mt-3 text-sm">
                    All development is done directly by our principal consultant. No offshore teams, no handoffs. You work with one person who understands your business and owns the entire solution.
                </p>
            </details>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Final CTA -->
    <section class="mt-8 md:mt-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-primary-dark text-white rounded-lg p-6 md:p-8 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Not Ready to Talk Yet?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">
            Explore our case studies to see real projects and measurable results.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a href="/portfolio/" class="btn bg-white text-primary hover:bg-gray-100">
                View Case Studies
            </a>
            <a href="/services/" class="btn bg-accent hover:bg-accent-dark text-white">
                See Our Services
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>
